name: I dare you
description:
‘I dare you’ is the first work in the FACES collection. It’s portraying someone who’s bold. She’s staring at the viewer in a daring way. This illustration captures the power and confidence of the person portrayed, as well as her roughness and sharp edges. 
Every illustration in this collection has its own identity. The colour combinations say something about the person portrayed: who they are and how they feel. And through the way they make eye contact or look away, these individuals tell their story.

Artwork made by Bo Stiemer.
